svg.text: - Built with React- Uses Redux- Allows users to take courses- Is our company homepage- Has an admin panel with tools to help our creators- Hosted on AWS Amplify
- Content Management System- Allows our creators to input the courses- Has a Graphql API Endpoint- Have a production and staging- Hosted on Elastic Beanstalk

- Most of the admin tools come to here for functions- Package generator for courses- Custom Scorm factors for customers- Color palette generator- Video to streaming converter- Bug report tracking system- Hosted using elastic beanstalk
- The outlet for all course tracking- Has course limits- Sends emails when limits have been hit- Course limits can be assigned on course, general or per key basis- Hosted on elastic beanstalk
- RDS Mysql Database- Prisma made and querried- Holds log data- Holds course limits data-Holds course limit transactions data- Holds course limit access code data
- RDS Mysql Databse- Managed by craft
